c: 31
v: 14
t: "Futhi samyala umuntu ukuthi enze okuhle kubona bobabili abazali bakhe, unina wayemkhulelwa ngobuthakathaka nangobunzima phezu kobuthakathaka nobunzima, ukukhumulwa kwakhe (ebeleni) kuseminyakeni emibili, bonga mina (Mvelinqangi) kanye nabazali bakho bobabili kukumina ukufinyelela kokugcina"